    <body>
      <lg type="song lyrics">
        <head>Rainy Day</head>
        <lg number="1" type="stanza">
          <l>Started walking alone </l>
          <l>As the train carried on </l>
          <l>Though I'll catch me a ride </l>
          <l>On the other side </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="2" type="stanza">
          <l>But you can never be sure </l>
          <l>What the day has in store </l>
          <l>When you trust on your luck </l>
          <l>What might turn up </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="3" type="stanza">
          <l>So I looked up </l>
          <l>So the sky turn black </l>
          <l>Before I could turn back </l>
          <l>The rain was all over me </l>
          <l>I wished that I could be </l>
          <l>Back Home </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="4" type="stanza">
          <l>So I ran to the road </l>
          <l>But there was no way to cross </l>
          <l>And get to the other side </l>
          <l>And catch a ride </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="5" type="stanza">
          <l>So I caved in </l>
          <l>'cause that moment seemed </l>
          <l>Like there wasn't anything </l>
          <l>That could get me out of here </l>
          <l>I condensed all my fear </l>
          <l>And screamed </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="6" type="stanza">
          <l>Haven't felt this alive </l>
          <l>Before that moment arrived </l>
          <l>Must be this will to survive </l>
          <l>That Cleared my eyes</l>
        </lg>
      </lg>
    </body>
